title: The Best Of The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: The Best Of The Dan Patrick Show
description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP discusses the Niners decision to name Trey Lance their starting QB. NFL Insider Ian Rapoport calls in to discuss uncovering the Kyler Murray having to study film 4 hours a week. And Ross Tucker shares which NFC team he thinks is most likely to miss the playoffs.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
